      <p>If you succeed, deal elemental damage equal to your ranks in Resolve to all creatures and dolls in the target spaces. You may remove dangerous, entangling, or obscuring terrain from each target space at no additional cost. You may also remove elevated terrain from any target space; any creature or doll that was in that elevated terrain suffers a critical strike.</p>
