      </ul>
    """
  },
  "Vampirism": {
    "rank": 1,
    "type": "Remolding",
    "approach": null,
    "skill": "Resolve",
    "flavor": """
      The remolding unit pulls energy out of a target and routes it back through you. Simple in principle. The enemy gets less; you get more. First lesson in applied remolding.
    """,
    "description": """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack action, make a <strong>TN 2 Resolve check</strong> targeting one enemy 1–3 range bands away.</p>
      <h3>Effects:</h3>
      <p>If you succeed, deal elemental damage to the target equal to your ranks in Resolve. You recover fatigue equal to your bonus successes.</p>
    """
  },
